Street Fighter Vs Mortal Kombat

	


This is a Mugen i found some where.  With nearly 60 characters it's sure to fun!
2 extra characters have also been added:

Rambo and a character called Orchid from an arcade game called 'Killer Instinct' (a personal fav of mine).









	

	How to Install:


	STEP 1:		Extract file with 7z to anywhere you like.
			(note: Game will install to 'OS':GamesSF_Vs_MK)


	STEP 2:		Double click 'setup.exe' in 'Street Fighter Vs 
                        Mortal Kombat' folder.


	STEP 3:		Follow on screen instructions!
			*DO NOT INTERRUPT PROCESS ONCE EXTRACTION HAS 
                        BEGUN*

	
	STEP 4:		Start game from Desktop.
